Package: keywords
Title: Keyword generation from PDFs using topic modeling
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "James",
           family = "Conigrave",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "james@conigrave.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8816-6229"))
Description: This package takes in PDF inputs and genrates keywords using topic modelling. Users can specfiy the numers of topics, and keywords per topic. Additionally a function is provided to create a systematic review flow diagram.
